quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,6,"“Ndithu amene sadakhulupirire, nchimodzimodzi kwa iwo uwachenjeze kapena usawachenjeze sangakhulupirire"
  2,7,"“(Ali ngati kuti) Allah wawadinda chidindo chotseka mitima yawo ndi makutu awo (kotero kuti kuunika kwa chikhulupiliro sikungalowemo), ndipo m’maso mwawo muli chophimba (sangathe kuona zozizwitsa za Allah); choncho iwo adzalandira chilango chachikulu"
  2,8,"“Pakati pa anthu alipo (anthu achinyengo) amene akunena: “Takhulupirira mwa Allah ndi tsiku lachimaliziro,” pomwe iwo sali okhulupirira"
  2,9,"“Akufuna kunyenga Allah ndi amene akhulupirira, ndipo sanyenga aliyense koma okha, ndipo iwo sazindikira (kuti akudzinyenga okha)"
  2,10,“M’mitima mwawo muli matenda; ndipo Allah wawaonjezera matenda. Choncho iwo adzalandira chilango chopweteka chifukwa cha bodza lawo
  2,11,"“Ndipo akauzidwa kuti: “Musaononge padziko,” amayankha kuti: “Ife ndife okonza.”"
  2,12,"“Dziwani kuti, ndithudi, iwo ndiwo ali oononga (pa dziko); koma sakuzindikira"
  2,13,"“Ndipo akauzidwa kuti, “Khulupirirani monga momwe anthu ena akhulupirira,” amayankha kuti: “Kodi tikhulupirire monga momwe zakhulupirira zitsiru?” Dziwani kuti, ndithudi, iwo ndi omwe ali zitsiru, koma sakudziwa"
  2,14,"“Ndipo akakumana ndi amene akhulupirira, amanena: “Takhulupirira.” Koma akakhala pa okha ndi asatana awo, amati: “Ndithudi ife tili pamodzi nanu. Timangowachita chipongwe basi.”"
  2,15,"“Allah adzawalipira chipongwe chawocho, ndipo akuwalekelera akungoyumbayumba (kugwira njakata) m’kusokera kwawo"
  2,16,"“Oterewo ndiomwe asinthanitsa chiongoko ndi kusokera, koma malonda awo sadawapindulire chilichonse, tero sadali oongoka"